real but not causal, since the same pattern recurs where the supposed mechanism is absent —as the evidence, read in full, requires.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Correct: its second sentence is the only one that satisfies the discriminating condition."}]'::jsonb, 'D', 'Logical Reconstruction:
